  "description": "A breathtaking view of a sunset over a bay, featuring a prominent bridge extending across the water. The sun is a brilliant orange orb, partially obscured by dark, dramatic clouds, creating a fiery and atmospheric sky. Below, the calm waters of the bay reflect the colors of the sunset, and a smaller island with a building is visible in the middle distance. Silhouetted trees frame the bottom of the image, adding depth and a natural element.  A shipping lane can be observed as a line of ships travel in the distance. The bridge itself is a steel structure with distinctive towers and suspension cables.",
